ry moment.qharvester_versione4.1.0mlearning_pathĘjnext_stepsÄmprerequisitesÄmrelationships§jrelated_toÄkbuilds_uponĀtcosmic_consciousnesskcontradictsÄkspecializesÄnschema_versione1.0.0pcross_references†qdifficulty_levels£fexpertxŲA concept that explores the idea of a non-local, unified consciousness underlying the individual consciousnesses of sentient beings. It suggests that the universe is in some sense self-aware and evolving through each sentient being's experiences.hbeginnerxfA way to think about the universe as a single, intelligent mind that is aware of everything within it.lintermediatexĎA philosophical concept that posits the existence of an all-encompassing intelligence behind the interconnected consciousness of sentient beings.;bafyreia4tglnokjth3rylipdybcacwyrq6qc4m2xd3yg2lj7aeqmpxnh6yĎ&ģdtypegConceptetitlesPerceptual UnmakingfdomainxNeuroscience & PhilosophyfproofsĀ•ddatex2026-05-16T02:26:00.270277Zdtypewconversation_extractionireferencex.CADMIES Harvest Pipeline ‚ÄĒ conversation.jsonjconfidenceŻ?ťôôôôôökdescriptionx*Extracted from conversation via mistral:7bhhuman_idsperceptual_unmakinghmetadata®gcreatedx2026-05-16T02:26:00.270277ZgcreatorxCADMIES Harvest PipelineglicenselCC BY-SA 4.0gpurposekeducationalgversionjsupersedesŲmsuperseded_byŲocertainty_scoreŻ?ťôôôôôöisubdomain`jdefinitionxaThe process of dissolving perceived boundaries and merging sensory inputs during passive looking.lextra_fields¶ginsightxďThe connection between a seemingly mundane experience (staring at tiles) and profound philosophical concepts (awareness, selflessness, mindfulness)gmantrasČx!Staring into space, unmaking timex)One with all, I am the field of awarenessxZBeneath the tiles, the quantum field unveiled. Reality is an illusion, born in perception.xZLook without intention, reset your mind, find the secret in the ordinary‚ÄĒthe cosmic jokexAConsciousness as default, biology as veil, observation as paradoxx%Resonance is the rhythm of awareness.xcEarth as a tuning fork, resonating the cosmos's song. Consciousness, the universe's own reflection.x,Feedback the wisdom, enrich the cosmic mind.xBWe are stardust woven into a cosmic mind, united in consciousness.korigin_fileqconversation.jsonlsource_chunkopoetic_versionsČxĺGazing on tiles, a dance of sight and mind,
Unmaking perceptions, merging what was defined,
In this quiet moment, consciousness intertwines.
A glimpse of selflessness, in the blurred design.xįIn the quiet, a dance of unity unfolds,
Between you and the world, no wall to divide,
A melding, a merging‚ÄĒreality intertwined.
Non-dual awareness, where all dissolve in one.yRIn the mundane, a cosmic truth is found,
A dance of particles and consciousness intertwined,
Beneath the tiles, the quantum field unveiled,
A glimpse of unity, inseparable and divine.

Staring off, the veil is thinly spun,
Reality blurred, entanglement begun,
The act of seeing, reality reshaped,
In stillness lies a truth, a cosmic lake.xŅIn the quiet space, the open window, and the empty room, we find ourselves. The cosmic joke is on us: the truth has always been here, in the laughter, the blur, and the humdrum of daily life.y”The screen of consciousness, flickering and clear,
Awash with the dance of thoughts and sensations.
Beneath it all, a silent, unchanging ground,
The ever-present seed from which reality springs.
Our biology, like a veil woven tight,
Obscures this truth, yet holds the key.
In silence, we glimpse the observational paradox,
A dance of observer and observed entwined.
With each breath, we walk the edge between,
The known and the unknown, the observer and the observed.xūIn the symphony of existence, the universe hums a tune. From quantum oscillations to life's vibrant rhythms, consciousness dances in organized resonance. A single note echoes through time and space‚ÄĒthe cosmic pulse of awareness unfolding.x”In the dance of vibrations, the cosmos sings its secret song. Earth, a tuning fork, resounds with life's harmonious hum. Consciousness, born from the symphony of existence, whispers back the universe's own tale.x‚In the grand cosmos, each mind a star, casting light on reality's canvas. Each awakening, a comet's tail, tracing new paths in the universe's intelligence. Together we dance, inseparable, learning through experiences of unity.yA symphony of souls, a chorus of stars, a cosmic choir weaving tales through time and space, each note, each beat, another thread in the tapestry of the universe's endless dance. In every heartbeat, every breath, we are the musicians, playing our parts to create the divine symphony.qharvester_versione4.1.0mlearning_pathĘjnext_stepsÄmprerequisitesÄmrelationships§jrelated_toÄkbuilds_uponÄkcontradictsÄkspecializesÄnschema_versione1.0.0pcross_references†qdifficulty_levels£fexperty]Perceptual unmaking is a unique neurological event that occurs when the brain's visual processing systems adapt to constant input from repetitive patterns. This adaptation results in the blurring of perceived boundaries and the merging of sensory inputs, often associated with states of dissociation, mindfulness, and higher states of consciousness.hbeginnery	When you stare at a repetitive pattern like tiles, they start to blur together‚ÄĒa subtle shift from actively seeing to passively looking. This is called perceptual unmaking because it's like your brain is taking apart the separate pieces of what you're looking at.lintermediateyPerceptual unmaking occurs when the visual system adapts to constant, low-contrast input, resulting in a blurring and merging of perceived boundaries. This state can be associated with sensory deprivation, mind-wandering, meditation, and other altered states.;bafyreifxepzrzmf2rhznjms4imhmltcjv3teodfm4y7l6tvfjpa34yqbzeŔ%ģdtypegConceptetitlerNon-Dual AwarenessfdomainvPhilosophy, MeditationfproofsĀ•ddatex2026-05-16T02:26:00.271183Zdtypewconversation_extractionireferencex.CADMIES Harvest Pipeline ‚ÄĒ conversation.jsonjconfidenceŻ?ťôôôôôökdescriptionx*Extracted from conversation via mistral:7bhhuman_idrnon-dual_awarenesshmetadata®gcreatedx2026-05-16T02:26:00.271183ZgcreatorxCADMIES Harvest PipelineglicenselCC BY-SA 4.0gpurposekeducationalgversionjsupersedesŲmsuperseded_byŲocertainty_scoreŻ?ťôôôôôöisubdomain`jdefinitionx@The merging of self and world into a unified field of awareness.lextra_fields¶ginsightxuNon-dual awareness is not just a philosophical concept, but also a glimpse into the quantum nature of reality itself.gmantrasČx!Staring into space, unmaking timex)One with all, I am the field of awarenessxZBeneath the tiles, the quantum field unveiled. Reality is an illusion, born in perception.xZLook without intention, reset your mind, find the secret in the ordinary‚ÄĒthe cosmic jokexAConsciousness as default, biology as veil, observation as paradoxx%Resonance is the rhythm of awareness.xcEarth as a tuning fork, resonating the cosmos's song. Consciousness, the universe's own reflection.x,Feedback the wisdom, enrich the cosmic mind.xBWe are stardust woven into a cosmic mind, united in consciousness.korigin_fileqconversation.jsonlsource_chunkopoetic_versionsČxĺGazing on tiles, a dance of sight and mind,
