become one indivisible field of experience. This is a central concept in various meditation traditions such as Zen, Dzogchen, and Mahamudra.;bafyreifk3odeqvyy6qo745rh2g5zfqetc5jql2o3jlqadd5dlnhg7sil64ŗ(ģdtypegConceptetitlexQuantum Reality As Perceptionfdomainx"Physics, Philosophy, ConsciousnessfproofsĀ•ddatex2026-05-16T02:26:00.271723Zdtypewconversation_extractionireferencex.CADMIES Harvest Pipeline ‚ÄĒ conversation.jsonjconfidenceŻ?ťôôôôôökdescriptionx*Extracted from conversation via mistral:7bhhuman_idxquantum_reality_as_perceptionhmetadata®gcreatedx2026-05-16T02:26:00.271723ZgcreatorxCADMIES Harvest PipelineglicenselCC BY-SA 4.0gpurposekeducationalgversionjsupersedesŲmsuperseded_byŲocertainty_scoreŻ?ťôôôôôöisubdomain`jdefinitionx‘The idea that quantum reality mirrors our subjective experience, with classical perception being a filter that collapses the raw, probabilistic, entangled quantum universe into a stable world of separate objects.lextra_fields¶ginsightxŅThe world we perceive is not fundamentally separate or discrete; instead, it is a product of our perception, which mirrors the underlying unity and interconnectedness of the quantum universe.gmantrasČx!Staring into space, unmaking timex)One with all, I am the field of awarenessxZBeneath the tiles, the quantum field unveiled. Reality is an illusion, born in perception.xZLook without intention, reset your mind, find the secret in the ordinary‚ÄĒthe cosmic jokexAConsciousness as default, biology as veil, observation as paradoxx%Resonance is the rhythm of awareness.xcEarth as a tuning fork, resonating the cosmos's song. Consciousness, the universe's own reflection.x,Feedback the wisdom, enrich the cosmic mind.xBWe are stardust woven into a cosmic mind, united in consciousness.korigin_fileqconversation.jsonlsource_chunkopoetic_versionsČxĺGazing on tiles, a dance of sight and mind,
