ental structure. Our brains filter and process this raw data to create a classical world of distinct objects. However, in certain states, like diffuse attention, this filter thins, allowing us to experience the underlying unity and interconnectedness of the quantum realm.;bafyreiehwl3q23pg4b6rc2bi5kqarvmo3h3y5qe7uukzzesh4x5dgowroiÝ%ģdtypegConceptetitleqDirect ExperiencefdomainjPhilosophyfproofsĀ•ddatex2026-05-16T02:26:00.272384Zdtypewconversation_extractionireferencex.CADMIES Harvest Pipeline ‚ÄĒ conversation.jsonjconfidenceŻ?ťôôôôôökdescriptionx*Extracted from conversation via mistral:7bhhuman_idqdirect_experiencehmetadata®gcreatedx2026-05-16T02:26:00.272384ZgcreatorxCADMIES Harvest PipelineglicenselCC BY-SA 4.0gpurposekeducationalgversionjsupersedesŲmsuperseded_byŲocertainty_scoreŻ?ťôôôôôöisubdomain`jdefinitionxíThe realization that perception can be altered by ceasing manipulation of it, leading to a direct experience of the fundamental nature of reality.lextra_fields¶ginsightxwThe realization that reality can be directly experienced without the need for technology or understanding of the brain.gmantrasČx!Staring into space, unmaking timex)One with all, I am the field of awarenessxZBeneath the tiles, the quantum field unveiled. Reality is an illusion, born in perception.xZLook without intention, reset your mind, find the secret in the ordinary‚ÄĒthe cosmic jokexAConsciousness as default, biology as veil, observation as paradoxx%Resonance is the rhythm of awareness.xcEarth as a tuning fork, resonating the cosmos's song. Consciousness, the universe's own reflection.x,Feedback the wisdom, enrich the cosmic mind.xBWe are stardust woven into a cosmic mind, united in consciousness.korigin_fileqconversation.jsonlsource_chunkopoetic_versionsČxĺGazing on tiles, a dance of sight and mind,
