r with reality. This notion challenges our traditional understanding of subjectivity and objectivity.;bafyreiga55rrja7a4mrqdwhokl7jquwtk2pfcsxz3cchytmtn3p5qhulfq√&ģdtypegConceptetitlemFactory ResetfdomainjPhilosophyfproofsĀ•ddatex2026-05-16T02:26:00.273057Zdtypewconversation_extractionireferencex.CADMIES Harvest Pipeline ‚ÄĒ conversation.jsonjconfidenceŻ?ťôôôôôökdescriptionx*Extracted from conversation via mistral:7bhhuman_idmfactory_resethmetadata®gcreatedx2026-05-16T02:26:00.273057ZgcreatorxCADMIES Harvest PipelineglicenselCC BY-SA 4.0gpurposekeducationalgversionjsupersedesŲmsuperseded_byŲocertainty_scoreŻ?ťôôôôôöisubdomain`jdefinitionx£The idea that enlightenment is not an upgrade but a return to a state of unburdened, clear awareness that precedes the formation of fixed ideas and heavy identity.lextra_fields¶ginsightxdThe idea that enlightenment is not an upgrade but a return to a state of pure, unburdened awareness.gmantrasČx!Staring into space, unmaking timex)One with all, I am the field of awarenessxZBeneath the tiles, the quantum field unveiled. Reality is an illusion, born in perception.xZLook without intention, reset your mind, find the secret in the ordinary‚ÄĒthe cosmic jokexAConsciousness as default, biology as veil, observation as paradoxx%Resonance is the rhythm of awareness.xcEarth as a tuning fork, resonating the cosmos's song. Consciousness, the universe's own reflection.x,Feedback the wisdom, enrich the cosmic mind.xBWe are stardust woven into a cosmic mind, united in consciousness.korigin_fileqconversation.jsonlsource_chunkopoetic_versionsČxĺGazing on tiles, a dance of sight and mind,
