 existed before the formation of fixed ideas and heavy identity. This notion challenges our conventional understanding of personal growth as an accumulation of knowledge and experiences.;bafyreihrvz6sqq7x7n53qahbvmklwr5ufml3ayqfkqlsf3tdtu55gppbmeĪ&ģdtypegConceptetitlekCosmic JokefdomainjPhilosophyfproofsĀ•ddatex2026-05-16T02:26:00.273580Zdtypewconversation_extractionireferencex.CADMIES Harvest Pipeline ‚ÄĒ conversation.jsonjconfidenceŻ?ťôôôôôökdescriptionx*Extracted from conversation via mistral:7bhhuman_idkcosmic_jokehmetadata®gcreatedx2026-05-16T02:26:00.273580ZgcreatorxCADMIES Harvest PipelineglicenselCC BY-SA 4.0gpurposekeducationalgversionjsupersedesŲmsuperseded_byŲocertainty_scoreŻ?ťôôôôôöisubdomain`jdefinitionxõThe ironic realization that the secret to understanding reality is hidden in plain sight, in ordinary human experiences such as daydreaming or spacing out.lextra_fields¶ginsightxĀThe realization that enlightenment is hidden in plain sight within ordinary human experiences such as daydreaming or spacing out.gmantrasČx!Staring into space, unmaking timex)One with all, I am the field of awarenessxZBeneath the tiles, the quantum field unveiled. Reality is an illusion, born in perception.xZLook without intention, reset your mind, find the secret in the ordinary‚ÄĒthe cosmic jokexAConsciousness as default, biology as veil, observation as paradoxx%Resonance is the rhythm of awareness.xcEarth as a tuning fork, resonating the cosmos's song. Consciousness, the universe's own reflection.x,Feedback the wisdom, enrich the cosmic mind.xBWe are stardust woven into a cosmic mind, united in consciousness.korigin_fileqconversation.jsonlsource_chunkopoetic_versionsČxĺGazing on tiles, a dance of sight and mind,
