fic vibrations might exhibit a form of 'awareness'.lintermediateyqResonance as Consciousness proposes that the organization and synchronization of vibrations in matter, such as in quantum fields or neurons, could contribute to conscious experience. This idea challenges traditional views of consciousness being solely associated with biological organisms and opens up intriguing possibilities for understanding the nature of awareness.;bafyreigojwbwr7cmku4hbirrjksabe45ss55bhtqu4mel7zwq2ndjbjtki‹$ģdtypegConceptetitlepCosmic ResonancefdomainjPhilosophyfproofsĀ•ddatex2026-05-16T02:26:00.276144Zdtypewconversation_extractionireferencex.CADMIES Harvest Pipeline ‚ÄĒ conversation.jsonjconfidenceŻ?ťôôôôôökdescriptionx*Extracted from conversation via mistral:7bhhuman_idpcosmic_resonancehmetadata®gcreatedx2026-05-16T02:26:00.276144ZgcreatorxCADMIES Harvest PipelineglicenselCC BY-SA 4.0gpurposekeducationalgversionjsupersedesŲmsuperseded_byŲocertainty_scoreŻ?ťôôôôôöisubdomain`jdefinitionxlThe idea that consciousness arises from organized, complex, and self-referential vibrations in the universe.lextra_fields¶ginsightxôThe universe might be observing and understanding itself through the emergence of consciousness in certain complex systems, such as Earth and life on it.gmantrasČx!Staring into space, unmaking timex)One with all, I am the field of awarenessxZBeneath the tiles, the quantum field unveiled. Reality is an illusion, born in perception.xZLook without intention, reset your mind, find the secret in the ordinary‚ÄĒthe cosmic jokexAConsciousness as default, biology as veil, observation as paradoxx%Resonance is the rhythm of awareness.xcEarth as a tuning fork, resonating the cosmos's song. Consciousness, the universe's own reflection.x,Feedback the wisdom, enrich the cosmic mind.xBWe are stardust woven into a cosmic mind, united in consciousness.korigin_fileqconversation.jsonlsource_chunkopoetic_versionsČxĺGazing on tiles, a dance of sight and mind,
