    To sow and reap without pocketing a cent,
    A harvest of knowledge where all may be met.

    Within this realm of cosmic play,
    We find truth and beauty on display,
    In quantum wiggles and cells at bay,
    The wonder of the universe held in sway.xýA seed in the ground, free to grow at its own pace, yet yearning for the sun's warmth and rain. A resilient dream, nurtured by volunteers, but longing for a gardener's touch. With just a little bit more, it could bloom, providing sustenance for all.ydA lean, agile team of visionaries‚ÄĒ
