To trace the winding thread of life divine.x≥A grand symphony of science, where physics whispers to enzymes, and ecology echoes back. Together they dance, weaving a tapestry of truth that spans the microscopic to the cosmic.xęFrom galaxies to quarks, a cosmic dance unfolds, 
