Our time on stage is running out,
Can we change before it's too late,
Before the mirror shows us our route?x•A mirror to reflect, a play to observe, a dance of particles weaving reality's tapestry. Collective self-awareness whispers its secrets in the echoes of our actions.xŔIn the vast expanse of existence, two paths diverged‚ÄĒone whispered in silence, the other roared with equations. Yet, both sought not the self but the unity that binds it all, like river and ocean merging at the sea.yūIn the mirror of our thoughts, a universe is born;
